                        <interp inst="t18390304-name-1077" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CRIPPS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a boat-master, and live at Uxbridge. The pri<lb></lb>soner was formerly in my service—I discharged him six month ago—I did not send him for any of this hay—I deal in hay and straw.</p>
